      <title>越南中央政治局委员因违反党规​​辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/vietnam-politburo-member-resigns-over-party-damaging-violations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南共产党批准了政治局委员张氏梅的辞职，这使她成为自 2022 年以来在腐败调查不断扩大的情况下第六位下台的政治局官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/vietnam-politburo-member-resigns-over-party-damaging-violations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 11:23:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
